  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785450/extras/f4c8311088649272a9606266900172a1.poster.avif?t=1659127933\" width=592 height=257 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785450/extras/f4c8311088649272a9606266900172a1.webm?t=1659127933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>In the future,<strong> fun has been deemed \"too dangerous\".</strong> Test your limits in jaw-dropping, body shaking action to save the world from boredom in this fast-paced <strong>sidescrolling shooter</strong>!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785450/extras/63344614e722dc3dc0686c5a89511a28.poster.avif?t=1659127933\" width=592 height=257 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785450/extras/63344614e722dc3dc0686c5a89511a28.webm?t=1659127933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Reign destruction with <strong>weapons and powerups beyond the ordinary.</strong> Battle through crazy locales from mile-tall factories to holy tree temples in the bizarre world of Strazeta.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785450/extras/27bb4726323c2d5d5c0b8222267bcd00.poster.avif?t=1659127933\" width=592 height=257 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785450/extras/27bb4726323c2d5d5c0b8222267bcd00.webm?t=1659127933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>Buy crazy add-ons and enhancements for your weapons and powerups.</strong> Earn Diamonds and spend them at the Upgrade Shop anytime. Want more? Crank up the challenge with <strong>fully adjustable difficulty settings. </strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785450/extras/701b7e1c5d599371da0c83274f235b31.poster.avif?t=1659127933\" width=592 height=257 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785450/extras/701b7e1c5d599371da0c83274f235b31.webm?t=1659127933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Earn score through completing <strong>unique mechanic objectives</strong>, from destroying stolen data to collecting holy blessings. These are hand-crafted and integrated to create a <strong>symphony of destruction and challenge.</strong>",
